    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-200 pt-4 !mt-10 border-t border-slate-800">
    Deployment & Infrastructure
  </h3>
  <p>
    The application is deployed using a distributed cloud infrastructure to ensure reliability and performance:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-2">
    <li><span class="font-bold text-slate-300">Frontend:</span> Hosted on <span class="text-slate-200 font-bold">Vercel</span> for fast, global delivery and seamless CI/CD.</li>
    <li><span class="font-bold text-slate-300">Backend:</span> The Spring Boot API is deployed on <span class="text-slate-200 font-bold">Render</span>.</li>
    <li><span class="font-bold text-slate-300">Database:</span> A managed PostgreSQL instance hosted on <span class="text-slate-200 font-bold">AWS RDS</span> ensures data persistence and security.</li>
  </ul>
